"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2019.10-2024.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系 教研系列准聘副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2014.10-2019.09<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系 副研究员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2008.10-2009.02　CERN　访问学者 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2006.11-2014.09<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>美国Syracuse University物理系 博士后</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">讲授《讲授《高能物理导论》本科生课程；讲授《高能物理实验专题》《粒子与核物理实验中的数据分析》《粒子物理》研究生课程，指导博士毕业生7名，在读博士生6名</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">现任清华大学粒子物理LHCb团队负责人。2006年获博士学位,期间以第一作者发表4篇高水平论文,在中性D介子混合领域取得早期突破。2006年赴美国雪城大学从事博士后研究,加入Sheldon Stone教授团队,成为味物理研究核心成员,合作发表23篇论文,并主导完成LHCb实验建成后的首批3篇论文。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2014年入选青年人才计划加入清华大学,任LHCb实验组骨干。2015年与合作者发现五夸克态,为核心分析人,首次提出并证实峰状结构为新粒子信号,成果引发国际关注。此后主导多项强子结构研究:发现五夸克态精细结构、奇异隐粲五夸克态证据、四夸克态Zcs(4000)+/Zcs(4220)+、X(3960)共振结构,以及粲介子D_s0(2590)+和底重子Ξ_b(6327/6333)^0等新激发态,多发表于《物理评论快报》。在CP破坏领域,创新方法将φs测量精度提升30%,保持LHCb国际领先地位。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">●&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">2024</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">—</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">2029</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">奇特强子态的实验研究</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">国家重点研发计划</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">项目负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2017年-2022年 五夸克态性质深入研究 国家重点研发计划 课题负责人</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. \"Improved measurement of CP violation parameters in Bs0 → J/ψK+K− decays in the vicinity of the φ(1020) resonance\", Phys. Rev. Lett. 132, 051802 (2024), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. \"Evidence of a J/ψKS0 structure in B0→J/ψφKS0 decays\", Phys. Rev. Lett. 131, 131901 (2023), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. \"Observation of a resonant structure near the Ds+Ds− threshold in the B+→ Ds+Ds−K+ decay\", Phys. Rev. Lett. 131, 071901 (2023), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4. \"Observation of two new excited Ξb0 states decaying to Λb0K−π+\", Phys. Rev. Lett. 128, 162001 (2022), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">5. \"A novel method to test particle ordering and final state alignment in helicity formalism\", Chin. Phys. C 45, 063103 (2021), Mengzhen Wang, Yi Jiang, Yinrui Liu, Wenbin Qian, Xiao-Rui Lyu, Liming Zhang.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">6. \"Observation of new resonances decaying to J/ψK+ and J/ψϕ\", Phys. Rev. Lett. 127, 082001 (2021), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">7. \"Evidence of a J/ψΛ structure and observation of excited Ξ− states in the Ξb− → J/ψΛK− decay\", Sci. Bull. 66, 1278 (2021), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">8. \"Observation of a new excited Ds+ meson in B0 → D+D−K+π− decays\", Phys. Rev. Lett. 126, 122002 (2021), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">9. \"Isospin amplitudes in Λb0 →J/ψΛ(Σ0) and Ξb0 →J/ψΞ0(Λ) decays\", Phys. Rev. Lett. 124, 111802 (2020), LHCb Collaboration.</span></p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2025年—今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>《Discovery Physics》编委会成员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2025年—今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>《Symmetry》编委会成员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2025年—今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>《Frontiers of Physics（物理学前沿）》编辑</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2023年—2025年<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>LHCb实验国际合作组“统计与机器学习”工作组负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2021年—2021年<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>LHCb实验国际合作组“优秀博士论文评选委员会”成员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2019年—2024年<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>LHCb实验国际合作组RTA项目中国组协调人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2019年—2021年<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>LHCb实验国际合作组“报告人遴选委员会(Speakers’Bureau)”成员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2016年—2018年<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>LHCb实验国际合作组“底强子到粲偶素衰变”物理工作组负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2025 &nbsp;基础物理学突破奖（作为LHCb合作组成员） Breakthrough Prize基金会</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2023 ‘青年服务国家’首都大学生暑期社会实践先进工作者 共青团北京市委员会</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2016 第二届“青年拔尖人才” &nbsp;中科院粒子物理前沿卓越创新中心</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2006 第四届“晨光杯”青年论文三等奖 高能物理学会</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2006 院长优秀奖 中科院</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span><br></p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"model-title\">\n                <div class=\"model\">常用链接</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"model-block\"></div>\n            <ul>\n      <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74493)\"><li>清华大学</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74494)\"><li>清华新闻网</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://tsinghua.cn.libguides.com/c.php?g=915369\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74495)\"><li>图书馆－核学科</li></a>\n</ul>\n            <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:41px;\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"copy-right-box\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:26px;\"></div>\n        <ul>\n            <script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/mp4video.js\"></script>\n<li>地址：清华大学工程物理系（刘卿楼）</li> \n<li>邮编：100084</li> \n<li>电话：010-62785727</li> \n<li>邮箱：gwbgs@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</li>\n        </ul>\n        <d